urlText: Trackwork between Hurstville and Central
content:
Saturday 26 to Monday 28 December
  • Buses replace all trains between Hurstville and Central. Some buses start and end at Redfern.
  • Express buses also run between stations Waterfall, Cronulla and Sutherland direct to Central.
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between Cronulla or Waterfall and Hurstville, and between Central and Bondi Junction.
  • If you are travelling: 
    • to the Airport, catch route 7AT4 to Wolli Creek or an express bus to Central, then change for a T8 Airport & South Line train.
    • from the City to Tempe, Arncliffe, Banksia, Rockdale, Kogarah, Carlton or Allawah please change at Redfern for an all-stations or limited stop bus. 
    • from the City to all other Illawarra or South Coast Line stations please change at Central for express or limited stop buses.

urlText: Buses replace trains between Wyong and Hornsby
content:
Saturday 16 to Sunday 17 January 
  • From 7.50pm Saturday until 5am Sunday, buses replace trains between Wyong and Hornsby.
  • Trains run between Newcastle Interchange and Wyong, and between Hornsby and Central, some to a changed timetable.
Bus routes

2ACN Hornsby, Berowra then all stations to Woy Woy and return
3CN All stations Hornsby to Hawkesbury River and return
5CN Hornsby, Berowra, Tuggerah, Wyong and return
51CN Woy Woy, then all stations to Wyong and return
61CN Hornsby, Berowra, Gosford, then all stations to Wyong and return
subtitle: Buses replace trains between Wyong and Hornsby

urlText: Buses replace trains between Bomaderry and Kiama
content:
Monday 11 January 
  • From 2am until 11.50am, buses replace trains between Bomaderry and Kiama.
  • Trains run between Kiama, Wollongong and Bondi Junction, some to a changed timetable. 
  • Some early morning buses extend to Oak Flats or Wollongong.
Bus routes

1SC Kiama, then all stations to Bomaderry and return
2SC Wollongong, then Kiama and return
5SC Kiama, then Bombo, Minnamurra, Shellharbour Junction, Oak Flats and return (bypassing Bombo in the Oak Flats direction)
6SC Wollongong, then all stations to Kiama and return (bypassing Shellharbour Junction, Minnamurra and Bombo)
subtitle: Buses replace trains between Bomaderry and Kiama
